WEBVTT

00:10:58.983 --> 00:11:00.682
I had an opportunity

00:11:00.706 --> 00:11:05.066
to fly over the Indonesian
island of Sumatra,

00:11:05.090 --> 00:11:07.758
and I saw with my own eyes

00:11:07.782 --> 00:11:09.939
the massive deforestation

00:11:09.963 --> 00:11:14.162
to make room for palm oil plantations.

00:11:15.178 --> 00:11:19.879
By the way, palm oil is included
in thousands of food products

00:11:19.903 --> 00:11:21.504
we eat every day.

00:11:21.528 --> 00:11:24.599
The global demand for palm oil
is just increasing.

00:11:26.168 --> 00:11:30.304
In Sumatra, I met smallholder farmers